Bridge Design Pattern:


Example: Video - Youtube , Netflix, Prime

All have 4k, 8k , HD etc.

But there is a Processing class with 4K, 8K,HD ..

We use ProceesingQuality interface  and Video interface

Composition: making one class's thing in another class



Proxy:  

It is like proxy server


Payment : Net banking, UPI ,cc, Cash payment (Real)..

The first three are Proxy


Composition: CashPayment is used in UPI and NetBanking classes..



So, here, Interface called payment with pay method

The classes NetBanking and UPIBanking implements the Payment

there is pay method in these classes also..


But CashPayment is actual one... so, we are creating Cash object in the two Classes NetBanking and UPIBanking... and then calling cash.pay()..


In the  main method, we are writing parent interface reference assigned to derived class object...

Payment reference to Upi and Netbanking objects..



